text: Md. Delwar Hossain is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Mymensingh-1. ==Career== Hossain was elected to parliament from Mymensingh-1 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1973. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:1st Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Md. Delwar Hossain
